casebody.data:
[The State, ex rel.] Walton, Appellant, v. Hunter, Judge, et al., Appellees.

[Cite as State, ex rel. Walton, v. Hunter (1991), 57 Ohio St. 3d 134.]

(No. 90-1967 Submitted January 8, 1991 Decided February 6, 1991.) William J. Walton, pro se. Charles L. Bartholomew, prosecuting attorney, for appellees.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
